12.2 Glossary
	•	Civic Node: Citizen-operated server validating network operations.
	•	CivicWatch: Gamified oversight system for auditing AI and governance.
	•	Forkable AI Models: Open-source models that can be modified to correct bias.
	•	Micro-Tax: Small percentage allocation from transactions/nodes to fund governance and oversight.

