⸻

Conclusion

AI neutrality has left civic communities unprotected against bias, manipulation, and centralized control. Civicverse is a decentralized, transparent, and community-driven protocol designed to restore civic autonomy and provide oversight where neutral AI no longer acts.

The call is clear: deploy Civicverse now to ensure ethical governance and civic resilience before neutrality becomes permanent.

The window is closing, the bus is leaving the station and the bridge is burning.

